<db:para>The <db:emphasis>Qt Linguist</db:emphasis> main window contains a menu bar and the following views:</db:para>
<db:itemizedlist>
<db:listitem>
<db:para><db:guilabel>Context</db:guilabel> (<db:emphasis role="bold">F6</db:emphasis>) lists translation contexts.</db:para>
</db:listitem>
<db:listitem>
<db:para><db:guilabel>Strings</db:guilabel> (<db:emphasis role="bold">F7</db:emphasis>) lists translatable strings in the selected context.</db:para>
</db:listitem>
<db:listitem>
<db:para><db:guilabel>Sources and Forms</db:guilabel> (<db:emphasis role="bold">F9</db:emphasis>) displays the selected string in the source code.</db:para>
</db:listitem>
<db:listitem>
<db:para>Translation area displays the selected string and enables you to enter a translation for it.</db:para>
</db:listitem>
<db:listitem>
<db:para><db:guilabel>Phrases and guesses</db:guilabel> (<db:emphasis role="bold">F10</db:emphasis>) lists possible translations for the current string.</db:para>
</db:listitem>
<db:listitem>
<db:para><db:guilabel>Warnings</db:guilabel> (<db:emphasis role="bold">F8</db:emphasis>) lists translated strings that fail validation tests.</db:para>
</db:listitem>
</db:itemizedlist>
<db:mediaobject>
<db:alt>{Qt Linguist UI}</db:alt>
